    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Alexs-Adventures-In-Numberland/dp/1526623994/ref=sr_1_1?keywords=alexs+adventures+in+numberland&qid=1676157919&s=books&sprefix=alexs+ad%2Cstripbooks%2C219&sr=1-1" target="_self">“Alex’s Adventures in Numberland”</a> is a wonderful rabbit hole to fall into (pun intended). Alex Bellos, the author, writes in such a way that introduces the history and complexities of mathematics in an intuitive and fun way. As a non-science major, Numberland was easily approachable and digestible.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">This book plays into the natural curiosity of human nature, showing how mathematics would be an inevitable discovery for our species. <br></br>On that same note, Bellos discusses the hurdles early humans faced as they began to explore and experiment with simple arithmetic. How does one represent nothing? As it turns out, the existence of zero is non-trivial.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><mark>What I appreciate the most about Numberland is the way it helps one develop mathematical intuition. Numberland makes one see the math in everyday life, and helped me to foster a new appreciation for math.</mark> This appreciation soon turned into excitement, and I was eager to approach puzzles and algebraic problems to brush up on my math skills.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Numberland is a wonderful adventure to go on with Alex, and the end of this 411 page journey will have you wishing there were more pages.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
